{"type": "article", "id": 24737, "title": "可旋转的工作桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-31T06:52:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153229prjyL3haxzeosIbD.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这张超长的桌子原本是为一个工作室打造的，来自塞尔维亚的设计团队Studio AUTORI 。它的一头是固定的，用白色的钢架支撑，对应的桌面可以接上了一个水池，而桌子的中间和另一头则装上了滚轮，可以绕着固定的一头旋转，很灵活。对于较大的工作间里的操作台是一个参考。<a href=\"http://autori.rs/en/roto/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153225QerCxDhN2MG6ZBuc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021532265D69YSJrQyFC27HE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153226d3rVSclkDso2TM8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153227bTXp7qYLKJCVru90.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153227wnSU3mldZMNoBJqA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75607181\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n"}